data.name: sqlInsertCommand1.CommandText
data.value: INSERT INTO [Route] ([Root_No], [Train_No], [Start_Station], [End_Station], [StartingStation_Arrival], [EndStation_Arrival], [Price_1stClasss], [Price_2ndClass], [Price_3rdClass]) VALUES (@Root_No, @Train_No, @Start_Station, @End_Station, @StartingStation_Arrival, @EndStation_Arrival, @Price_1stClasss, @Price_2ndClass, @Price_3rdClass); SELECT Root_No, Train_No, Start_Station, End_Station, StartingStation_Arrival, EndStation_Arrival, Price_1stClasss, Price_2ndClass, Price_3rdClass FROM Route WHERE (Root_No = @Root_No)
